This directory contains a third-party asset vendored into pidgin and
redistributed under the MIT License.

Vendored asset:
  typebox-1.1.38.mjs
    upstream:  typebox (npm), version 1.1.38
    homepage:  https://github.com/sinclairzx81/typebox
    author:    Haydn Paterson (sinclair)

How it was produced:
  typebox 1.1.38's root export (its package "." entry, ./build/index.mjs) is a
  multi-file ES-module graph (~690 .mjs files). It was bundled into this single,
  self-contained ESM file with esbuild 0.28.1:

    npx esbuild build/index.mjs --bundle --format=esm --platform=neutral \
      --outfile=typebox-1.1.38.mjs

  Bundling to one file (no internal relative imports left to resolve) lets
  pidgin's extension module loader serve typebox as a single asset. The named
  export `Type` (and `Type.Object(...)`) is preserved; verified in Node before
  vendoring. A first-line straitjacket-allow-file marker was prepended so the
  bundled machine-generated JS does not trip the repo's source linters; the
  bundle body is otherwise the unmodified esbuild output.

  The asset is served by pidgin's deno extension module loader
  (crates/pidgin-extensions/src/module_loader.rs) for the bare specifiers
  `typebox` and `@sinclair/typebox`, mirroring pi's jiti virtualModules alias.

